B.Zg=new A.m(B.x,"Yakla\u015fma ifade kal\u0131plar\u0131 y\xfcksek d\xfczeyde yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r","Yakla\u015fma ve ini\u015f faz\u0131, havac\u0131l\u0131kta en \xe7ok d\xfczenlenen ifade kal\u0131plar\u0131n\u0131 kullan\u0131r. Yakla\u015fma s\u0131ras\u0131ndaki yanl\u0131\u015f anla\u015f\u0131lmalar kazalara neden oldu\u011fundan kesin dil \u015fartt\u0131r.\n\nBu alandaki bo\u015fluk doldurma sorular\u0131, tam ICAO ifadelerine ve do\u011fru edatlarla anahtar kelimelerine ili\u015fkin bilgiyi \xf6l\xe7er.",null,null,null)
