B.RW=new A.a2("We remind you that this is a non-smoking flight. Smoking is prohibited throughout the aircraft, including the lavatories.","Bu u\xe7u\u015fun sigara i\xe7ilmeyen bir u\xe7u\u015f oldu\u011funu hat\u0131rlat\u0131r\u0131z. Tuvaletler dahil olmak \xfczere u\xe7ak i\xe7inde sigara i\xe7mek yasakt\u0131r.","is prohibited")
