B.a0k=new A.m(B.v,"\ud83e\ude7a Temel T\u0131bbi Terimler","**Bilin\xe7 durumu:**\n\u2022 conscious / unconscious \u2014 bilin\xe7li / bilin\xe7siz\n\u2022 responsive / unresponsive \u2014 tepki veriyor / vermiyor\n\u2022 disoriented \u2014 dezoryantasyon\n\n**Belirtiler:**\n\u2022 chest pain \u2014 g\xf6\u011f\xfcs a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131\n\u2022 shortness of breath / dyspnea \u2014 nefes darl\u0131\u011f\u0131\n\u2022 nausea / vomiting \u2014 bulant\u0131 / kusma\n\u2022 seizure \u2014 n\xf6bet\n\u2022 anaphylaxis \u2014 anafilaksi (ciddi alerjik reaksiyon)\n\u2022 hypoglycemia \u2014 hipoglisemi (d\xfc\u015f\xfck kan \u015fekeri)\n\n**M\xfcdahale:**\n\u2022 administer oxygen \u2014 oksijen ver\n\u2022 AED (Automated External Defibrillator) \u2014 otomatik harici defibrilat\xf6r\n\u2022 first aid kit \u2014 ilk yard\u0131m \xe7antas\u0131\n\u2022 Is there a doctor or medical professional on board?",null,null,null)
